metadata.name: Birbz #1
metadata.description: Birbz is a 10k PFP collection that was launched during the crazy NFT spring of 2022. Handcrafted in 36x scale and resized to 360x. Heavily inspired by expensive mints, moons and yachts. No discord. No roadmap. Just Birbz. cc0. Birbz smart-contract acts as a Vending Machine and all the BIRB tokens are minted by sending ETH straight to the contract address, 0.01ETH/BIRB. *not affiliated with any Meme Labs*
